                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-125rb)&#xD;
- Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 2ra-8rb)&#xD;
- Maṣḥaf za-waḍʾāt ʾǝm-ʾIyarusālem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 20ra-22ra)&#xD;
- Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 55vb-60ra)&#xD;
- Homily by archbishop ʾabbā Sawiros (fols. 70va-72vb)&#xD;
- Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 81vb-85vb)&#xD;
- Antiphons (ʾaryām, mawāśǝʾt and mǝlṭān) (fols. 121ra-125rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
